6. EXCEPTIONS

6.1. Small Business Exception - Organizations with 15 or fewer machines using Light-Scan internally are exempt from the Commercial License requirement for internal business operations only, provided:

· (a) They are not distributing the Software to third parties
· (b) They are not offering it as a service to external customers
· (c) They are not integrating it into products sold to external customers
· (d) They are not using it for paid consulting or professional services

Any of the activities in (a)-(d) require a Commercial License regardless of machine count.

